# Environment files — never commit any .env or .env.* file
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!infra/.env.template

# Self-hosted infrastructure — NEVER commit.
# infra/ contains the Hetzner deploy stack: docker-compose.yml, Caddyfile,
# Postgres tuning, generated Supabase JWT secret + service-role key, kong
# config, etc. Blanket-ignored so a stray `git add infra/` cannot leak
# secrets. The exception below allows the secret-free template to be
# explicitly tracked if you ever want to.
infra/*
!infra/.env.template
dumps/
.env.local.backup-managed

# Dependencies and build artifacts
node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
.DS_Store

# Backups and generated evidence-import caches
backups/
data/

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Scratch / experimental work — never deploy
tmp/

# Git worktrees (isolated feature-branch workspaces)
.worktrees/

# Superpowers plugin cache — per-session working state, not code
.superpowers/

# Graphify knowledge-graph output — regenerated from source on demand,
# source of truth is the code it was built from, not this directory
graphify-out/

# Claude Code per-machine settings (permissions, local config).
# Never belongs in the repo — each dev has their own grants.
.claude/

# AI memory / project-scope satellite docs — kept local-only by
# convention. CLAUDE.md is the entry point; the rest are deep-dive
# references the AI reads when working on unfamiliar subsystems.
CLAUDE.md
changelog.md
checkpoint.md
docs/overview.md
docs/schema.md
docs/scripts.md
docs/references/

# Generic local-only workspace. Dump notes, scratch files, downloaded
# references, etc. here — nothing under .local/ will be committed.
.local/

# Obvious local-only junk (dated backups, scratch-named assets).
script.js.landing-backup-2026-04-11
assets/Untitled-2.png

# Local-only assets and working files (kept on disk, not on GitHub).
# Source .ai file not referenced in production HTML/JS/CSS.
assets/tutorial.ai
# Marketing spreadsheet is a personal working tracker, not a team doc.
Marketing/
# Large upscaled hero image not referenced in production.
neuron-hero-upscaled.png
# Ad-hoc internal review drafts (email-mockups/ subdir stays tracked).
internal/wedge-review-*.html
# Plans that were authored locally but aren't intended for the public repo.
docs/superpowers/plans/2026-04-16-progress-charts.md
